# ── Rust build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Biggest offenders: voice/engine/target (~25 GB), voice/server/target (~3.4 GB),
# integrations/target (~2.8 GB). BuildKit cache mounts in the Dockerfiles handle
# incremental Rust builds inside the container — local target/ is never needed.
**/target/

# ── Python / uv ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.venv/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/

# ── Node / Frontend ───────────────────────────────────────────────
studio/web/node_modules/
studio/web/.next/
studio/web/.turbo/

# ── Version control ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/

# ── Env / secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env*
!.env.example

# ── Editor / OS noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
.claude/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
